  "prompt": "Is there any good institute for differently abled child near Noida areas?",
  "response": "Yes, there are several reputable institutes and schools in and around the Noida area that cater to differently-abled children. Some of these include:\n\n1. **MBCN (Mata Bhagwanti Chadha Niketan)**:\n   - Location: Sector 132, Noida\n   - Description: It is a specialized school dedicated to serving children with intellectual and developmental disabilities. They offer a range of therapies, educational programs, and vocational training.\n\n2. **Sparsh Special School**:\n   - Location: Noida\n   - Description: Sparsh Special School provides tailored educational and therapeutic services for children with special needs. They focus on individualized learning plans and various forms of therapy.\n\n3. **Astha Special School**:\n   - Location: Noida\n   - Description: Astha Special School provides education and care to children with developmental and intellectual challenges, emphasizing individualized attention and skill development.\n\n4. **Nayi Disha Resource Centre**:\n   - Location: They may not be physically based in Noida but offer support and resources via their platform which can be helpful to parents and caregivers.\n   - Description: An organization that provides resources, guidance, and support for parents of children with developmental disabilities, including autism, ADHD, and cerebral palsy.\n\n5. **Sun International School**:\n   - Location: Noida\n   - Description: While not exclusively for differently-abled children, Sun International School offers inclusive education programs that integrate children with special needs into mainstream classrooms with appropriate support services.\n\nWhen considering a school or institute for a differently-abled child, it's essential to visit the facilities, meet the staff, and ensure the educational and therapeutic needs of your child will be addressed effectively.",
